Rendell E. de Kort {#title}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Development Economist & Regional Coordinator

Development economist with 15 years of experience spanning disaster risk management, regional coordination, and policy advisory across the Caribbean. Currently coordinating multi-island digital initiatives and serving as World Bank consultant on disaster risk financing.

